H0.text: Asexual reproduction is the process during which genetic material comes from two parents.

H1.text: Photosynthesis is the process during which genetic material comes from two parents.

H2.text: Respiration is the process during which genetic material comes from two parents.

H3.text: Sexual reproduction is the process during which genetic material comes from two parents.

A4.text: During sexual reproduction, two haploid gametes combine into one diploid cell known as a zygote in a process called fertilization.
